      "para_id": "Q002009.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Nergal of Apiak , the respected lord , the powerful lion , his master , Warad-Nanna , the royal scribe , child of Piqqum , his servant , dedicated this ( lion statue ) for the well being Damiq-ilišu , king of Sumer and Akkad ."
    }
  ],
